==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bosporus
<hw>Bos"po*rus</hw> <pr>(b⟦ocr⟧s"p⟦osl⟧*r⟦ucr⟧s)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[L.]</ety> <def>A strait or narrow sea between two seas, or a lake
and a seas; <as>as, the <ex>Bosporus</ex> (formerly the Thracian
Bosporus) or Strait of Constantinople, between the Black Sea and Sea of
Marmora; the Cimmerian <ex>Bosporus</ex>, between the Black Sea and Sea
of Azof</as>.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>Bosphorus</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bosquet</ent>⟦br⟧
